title: Saudagar
subTitle: Moti betrays his loyal wife and business partner, Majubee, to marry his true love, Phoolbanu. However, his selfish act unleashes unforeseen consequences that upend his life.

title: Clerk
subTitle: Bharat, a poor but honest clerk, sells state secrets under pressure from his family's financial dependence. Realizing his mistake, he chooses to fight and make things right.

title: Ek Musafir Ek Hasina
subTitle: A runaway bride meets a charming stranger and falls in love with him while tending to his wounds. However, when the man meets with an accident leading to amnesia, he completely forgets her.

title: Dulhan
subTitle: A girl is left distraught by the sudden death of her husband on their wedding night. However, things take a turn when a man resembling her husband arrives in the village.

title: Roop Tera Mastana
subTitle: Usha, a princess, is killed by her personal secretary Ajith. Later, Ajith coerces a woman who is an exact replica of the princess to pose as her in order to steal her wealth.

title: Bhagwan Dada
subTitle: Bhagwaan, a reformed criminal, rescues Swaroop, a naive villager. Swaroop rescues Bijli, a young woman targeted by Shambu. The situation regresses when Shambu decides to exact revenge.

title: Tamacha
subTitle: Raju and Vicky, two childhood friends, reunite after years apart. However, they end up on opposing sides of the law as Raju becomes a crusading officer, while Vicky descends into a life of crime.

title: Tyagi
subTitle: Shankar, a good man, takes the blame when one of his brothers is accused of a murder. However, when he returns from jail, he realises that his brothers are trying to create a rift in the family.

title: Andheri Raat Mein Diya Tere Haath Mein
subTitle: Two friends join the underworld to make money and to lead a comfortable life. Later, they realise the ill-effects of crime and want to lead a normal life.

title: Andheri Raat Mein Diya Tere Haath Mein
subTitle: Two friends join the underworld to make money and to lead a comfortable life. Later, they realise the ill-effects of crime and want to lead a normal life.

title: Naach Uthe Sansaar
subTitle: A rich man's daughter falls in love with a farmer and wants to marry him. However, her father not only disapproves of this but also humiliates his mother, which makes the farmer seek vengeance.

title: Pyar Kiye Jaa
subTitle: Ramlal, a widower, struggles to find suitable grooms for his daughters and to control his son's film obsession. To make matters worse, one of his former employees launches a protest against him.

title: Jawani Diwani
subTitle: Vijay meets Neeta, the daughter of a Thakur, and falls in love with her. However, things change after he finds out that she has been promised to another man in marriage.

title: Purab Aur Pachhim
subTitle: Bharat, a freedom fighter's son, travels to England to study and strives to change the mindset of the people there towards India.

title: Aakhree Raasta
subTitle: A man is falsely accused of his wife's murder and imprisoned. When he sets out to seek revenge, he finds a police officer on his trail who turns out to be his own son.

title: Amrit
subTitle: A widowed man and woman face abuse from their respective children and seek comfort from each other instead.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Caravan
subTitle: Sunita, a young woman, flees from her abusive marriage when her husband tries to kill her. She joins a travelling gypsy caravan en route to Bangalore and falls in love with its driver, Mohan.

title: Caravan
subTitle: Sunita, a young woman, flees from her abusive marriage when her husband tries to kill her. She joins a travelling gypsy caravan en route to Bangalore and falls in love with its driver, Mohan.

title: Awaara
subTitle: Born into poverty, Raj steals and works for a criminal gang in order to feed his mother. But when he meets and falls in love with his childhood friend, Rita, he vows to change his ways.

title: Biwi O Biwi
subTitle: To overcome with his love for Asha, singer Chandermohan masquerades as an army officer when her father, a retired military officer, refuses to let her marry a civilian.

title: Piya Ka Ghar
subTitle: Malti falls in love with Ram and marries him without knowing what to expect. When she goes to his house, she realises that he is very poor and she is stuck with him for the rest of her life.

title: Sangam
subTitle: Two best friends, Sundar and Gopal, love the same woman, Radha, while she has feelings only for Gopal. But when Sundar marries Radha, the love triangle is thrown into turmoil.

title: Saudagar
subTitle: Moti betrays his loyal wife and business partner, Majubee, to marry his true love, Phoolbanu. However, his selfish act unleashes unforeseen consequences that upend his life.

title: Mera Naam Joker
subTitle: Raju faces many hurdles and disappointments in matters of the heart throughout his life. But as a clown in a circus, he tries to make his audience laugh at the cost of his own sorrows.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: Suraj
subTitle: King Vikram arranges his daughter Anuradha's match with his commander's son Pratap. However, trouble strikes when Anuradha is abducted by a bandit Suraj when she goes to attend Pratap's coronation.
